            "title": "盤中速報 - 華納兄弟探索(WBD-US)大跌5.04%，報12.15美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華納兄弟探索(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WBD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WBD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WBD-US</a>)截至台北時間07日21:37股價下跌0.65美元，報12.15美元，跌幅5.04%，成交量5,645,418（股），盤中最高價13.23美元、最低價12.15美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.52%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.61%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.86%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+2.32%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>華納兄弟探索(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WBD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WBD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WBD-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-3.54%</li> <li>近 1 月：+13.99%</li> <li>近 3 月：+51.72%</li> <li>近 6 月：+25.39%</li> <li>今年以來：+21%</li></ul></section></main>",
